<item>
            <title>[SYNAPSE-1039] Send Mediator inside Fault Sequence blocks if SSL exception occurred.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-1039</link>
                <project id="12310201" key="SYNAPSE">Synapse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If SSL related exception occurred within a proxy service or sequence and if it is configured with Fault Sequence then if custom payload created inside fault sequence and trying to send the message to external service is blocked and timeout occurs at client side. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Issue can be reproduced by loading following artifacts. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;proxy xmlns=&quot;http://ws.apache.org/ns/synapse&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
       name=&quot;TestProxy&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
       transports=&quot;https,http&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
       statistics=&quot;disable&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
       trace=&quot;disable&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
       startOnLoad=&quot;true&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;target faultSequence=&quot;MyFaultSequency&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;inSequence&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &amp;lt;log level=&quot;full&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &amp;lt;send&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;endpoint&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
               &amp;lt;address uri=&quot;https://localhost:8088/mockssl&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;/endpoint&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &amp;lt;/send&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;/inSequence&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;outSequence&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &amp;lt;log&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;property name=&quot;OutSequence&quot; value=&quot;***** OUT **************&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
         &amp;lt;/log&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;send/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;/outSequence&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;/target&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;description/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/proxy&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;sequence xmlns=&quot;http://ws.apache.org/ns/synapse&quot; name=&quot;MyFaultSequency&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;log&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;property name=&quot;faultSequence&quot; value=&quot;****&lt;b&gt;Inside fault sequence&lt;/b&gt;****&quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/property&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;/log&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;header name=&quot;Action&quot; scope=&quot;default&quot; value=&quot;http://www.webserviceX.NET/ConversionRate&quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/header&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;send receive=&quot;RespondSeq&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;endpoint&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
               &amp;lt;address uri=&quot;http://localhost:8088/mock&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;/endpoint&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;/send&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/sequence&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;sequence xmlns=&quot;http://ws.apache.org/ns/synapse&quot; name=&quot;RespondSeq&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;log&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
      &amp;lt;property name=&quot;faultSequence&quot; value=&quot;****&lt;b&gt;Inside fault respond sequence&lt;/b&gt;****&quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/property&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;/log&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
   &amp;lt;send/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/sequence&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
